title: Weirdest Matchups
body:
Ok... So I was just playing a game, and I ended up Jax as support. This isn't so bad...
So we loaded in and the matchup was Tristana and Jax vs Caitlyn and Udyr...
Anyone seen a weirder matchup?

replies.body:
Now I'm in a game on Summoners Rift against Quinn, Ezreal, Lux, Xerath and Zed. No jungler...
EDIT: So... They all went mid and rushed the turret... They got that about 3 minute in... Me and the adc pushed top and bot, while the rest held mid.
We won...
